comment: Barnes (MEM) grabs Lillard's (POR) arm, affecting his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Referees communicated with the Replay Center and determined that the contact by Barnes (MEM) at 1:55 does not meet the criteria for a Flagrant
Lillard (POR) is in legal guarding position and outside the restricted area when he takes Conley's (MEM) charge.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Lillard (POR) was not in the restricted area when contact occurred with Conley (MEM) was upheld.
Conley (MEM) maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Lillard (POR).
Green (MEM) and Davis (POR) briefly engage and separate while rebounding.
Henderson (POR) makes contact to the arm of Allen (MEM) that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Barnes (MEM) makes contact to the off arm of Lillard (POR) after the shot had been released.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Green (MEM) committed offensive interference on the last second tip-in was overturned and the referees confirmed the tip-in occurred before the game clock expired.
Allen (MEM) impedes McCollum's (POR) movement by grabbing his hand.
Davis (POR) maintains legal guarding position and does not affect the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Randolph (MEM).
Davis (POR) makes contact with Randolph (MEM) that affects his RBSQ as he starts his dribble.
Davis (POR) pushes Randolph (MEM) into Barnes (MEM).
Aminu (POR) maintains legal guarding position and does not affect the shot attempt by Conley (MEM).
LHH shows Lillard (POR) and Barnes (MEM) briefly engage under the rim for the rebound.

LHH shows Davis (POR) jumps vertically before contact occurs with Conley (MEM) on his shot attempt and L-slash shows he does not make any contact to Conley's wrist or arm when he attempts to block the shot.
The Grizzlies do not get the shot off prior to the 24 second shot clock expiring.
Aminu (POR) establishes a position in Allen's (MEM) path, giving him room to avoid the contact on the screen and absorbing the contact when it occurs.
Randolph (MEM) and Davis (POR) briefly engage and separate on the missed shot.
Banres (MEM) touches the ball while it is still in the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
RATR shows that McCollum (POR) maintains a legal dribble, his off-hand coming close to, but not touching the ball while he is dribbling.
Barnes (MEM) commits the take foul on Davis POR).
Barnes (MEM) commits the take foul on Lillard (POR).
Conley (MEM) commits the take foul on Davis (POR).
